Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.80,0:21:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有可能以磁星开始自己的人生{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}may begin their lives as magnetars...{\r}
