Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.94,0:21:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}最终变成了普通的脉冲星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that eventually become normal pulsars...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}其实在经历磁星式爆发时{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}actually go through magnetar-like outbursts...{\r}
