Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.30,0:42:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它是某种反引力{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's sort of an anti-gravity.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.17,0:42:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}普通物质和能量趋向于减缓{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Normal matter and energy tend to slow down the rate...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.93,0:42:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}物体相互之间分开的速度{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}at which things are going away from each other...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.18,0:42:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为普通物质彼此之间有引力的吸引{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}because normal things pull on one another gravitationally.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.56,0:42:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是暗能量表现出{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But dark energy appears to accelerate the rate...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.27,0:42:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}加快物体彼此之间拉开的速度{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}at which objects pull away from each other.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.27,0:42:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有一个理论认为暗能量{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}One theory suggests that dark energy...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.78,0:42:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}将会加速空间的膨胀到这样一个程度{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}will accelerate the expansion of space to such an extent...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.24,0:43:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}整个宇宙将在500亿年里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that the entire universe will be ripped to shreds...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.12,0:43:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}被扯成碎片{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}in about 50 billion years.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.62,0:43:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果是那种情形 那么最终{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}If that's the case, then eventually...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.75,0:43:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不仅仅星系团会被相互扯开{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}not only will clusters of galaxies be ripped apart from one another...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.33,0:43:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而且星系本身也会被扯碎{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and then galaxies themselves will get ripped apart...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.92,0:43:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}恒星相互之间快速远离{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}as the stars zip away from one another.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.46,0:43:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}于是太阳系{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And then solar systems...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.92,0:43:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}行星系也将被扯碎{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}planetary systems will get ripped apart.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.22,0:43:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}于是接下来 甚至行星都将被扯碎{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And then, later on, even planets will get ripped apart...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.30,0:43:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}人类也将撕得粉身碎骨{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and humans will get ripped apart.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.18,0:43:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}最终 甚至原子和亚原子粒子都将被撕得粉碎{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And finally, even atoms and subatomic particles will get ripped apart.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.31,0:43:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}宇宙充满了千奇百怪的东西{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The universe is full of odd and interesting things...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.07,0:43:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是宇宙间最怪异的东西{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}but the most peculiar thing in the universe...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.19,0:43:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有可能就在我们的后院{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}may exist in our own backyard.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.11,0:43:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}毫无疑问 最怪异的东西{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}By far and away the strangest thing...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.78,0:43:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在我看来 在宇宙间就是地球{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}in my opinion, in the universe is Earth...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.37,0:43:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我生于斯 长于斯 我了解其一二{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and I live here, and I know something about it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.37,0:43:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这真是个怪异之地{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}What a crazy place this is.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.62,0:43:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}岩质行星 靠近恒星 布满绿色{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}A rocky planet, near a star with all this green stuff...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.46,0:43:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}获取阳光 变成食物{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that takes sunlight and turns it into food.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.09,0:44:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}多怪异啊 但是 知道吗 对别人来说{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}That's strange but, you know, to others...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.47,0:44:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一点都没有什么特别之处 因为它是家园{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}there's nothing particularly peculiar because it's home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.68,0:44:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我说啊 外太空里最怪异的东西就是人类{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I'd say the strangest things in outer space are human beings.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.44,0:44:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们确实不同凡响{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We're definitely unusual...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.85,0:44:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}迄今为止 我们在宇宙间还没有发现{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and we haven't found any other beings like us yet...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.81,0:44:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有任何其它东西如我们这样{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}in the universe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.86,0:44:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}尽管那并不是说它们不存在{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Although that's not to say that they aren't out there...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.98,0:44:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是我们非常怪异{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}but we're pretty strange.{\r}
